---
import Layout from '../components/Layout.astro';
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="About">
  <section class="py-20 bg-teal-50/30">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About Axis Seek</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mb-12">
          We are passionate about bringing innovative technology solutions to enhance your daily life.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Our Story</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
            Founded with a vision to bridge the gap between cutting-edge technology and everyday usability, 
            Axis Seek has been at the forefront of innovation since our inception. We believe that technology 
            should not only be advanced but also accessible and intuitive for everyone.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Our team of dedicated professionals works tirelessly to curate and develop products that make a 
            real difference in people's lives. From smart home solutions to personal wellness devices, we're 
            committed to delivering excellence in every product we offer.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 rounded-lg p-12 flex items-center justify-center">
          <div class="text-[200px] opacity-60">🚀</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="mt-20 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">🎯</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Our Mission</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            To provide innovative, high-quality technology products that enhance and simplify daily life.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">👁️</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Our Vision</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            To be the leading destination for discovering and experiencing the future of technology.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div>
          <div class="text-5xl mb-4">💎</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Our Values</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">
            Innovation, quality, customer satisfaction, and sustainable practices guide everything we do.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>